This paper discusses the integration of privacy considerations into the design of IoT applications, which is a topic related to cybersecurity (cs.CR) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also explores the challenges in using a Privacy-by-Design framework, which is a topic related to cyber law and policy (cs.CY), information retrieval (cs.IR), and social and information networks (cs.SI). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.CR and cs.SE, followed by cs.CY, cs.IR, and cs.SI.
